                    <span class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-emerald-500 shadow-[0_0_10px_rgba(16,185,129,0.5)]"></span> Systems Active</span>
                    <span class="flex items-center gap-2"><i class="bi bi-shield-check text-indigo-400"></i> Encrypted Mode</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

